Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.74,0:01:30.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.97,0:01:33.11,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知らないフリしたって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:34.17,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be My Side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:36.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部気づいてたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:40.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう一歩  君のとなりに行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.13,0:01:44.01,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その手にだって届きそうさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:54.12,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像以上だね  ジェットコースターな毎日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:02:00.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必死で前を向いて  いつも駆け抜け来たんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:09.60,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっと続きはしないね  僕らの時間は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:15.83,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今しかないから  この瞬間刻み付けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:17.11,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:19.46,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知らないフリしたって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:20.55,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be My Side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.84,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部気づいてたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:26.81,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう一歩  君のとなりに行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:29.48,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手を取れるように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:30.45,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.74,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見上げてばかりだって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:33.75,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be My Side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:36.03,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憧れてる  今も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:40.62,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう一回  何度でも手を伸ばそう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:44.10,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの星だって届きそうさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.74,0:01:30.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.97,0:01:33.11,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再装傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:34.17,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be My Side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:36.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经都察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:40.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一步  就能来到你的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.13,0:01:44.01,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能用我的手触碰到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:54.12,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是超乎想象呢  如同过山车般的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:02:00.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓足精神前进  一直都风风火火的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:09.60,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但属于我们的时光总是那么短暂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:15.83,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然时间转瞬即逝  那就铭记这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:17.11,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:19.46,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再装傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:20.55,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be My Side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.84,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经都察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:26.81,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一步  就能来到你的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:29.48,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能握住你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:30.45,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.74,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬起头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:33.75,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be My Side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:36.03,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所憧憬的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:40.62,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次  无论多少次都会伸出手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:44.10,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是那颗星星也触手可及
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.36,0:00:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.28,0:00:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你十年前的梦境里  为什么会出现夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,额  你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.74,0:00:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在睡眠状态下的小鹰学长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使劲地在「夜空  夜空」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.74,0:00:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出现在小鹰十年前的梦里也没什么好奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们是青梅竹马啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青梅竹马？小鹰和你？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  在小鹰十年前离开这个城市之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他经常在一起玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.69,0:00:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是所谓的青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.05,0:00:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.01,0:00:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你一直没说过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也不是什么值得到处宣扬的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:01:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小鹰以前是朋友  仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也隐约感觉到  朋友…曾是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇行少女不会受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有谁有疑问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟平时一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  在学园祭展出的就决定是妹抖咖啡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  差不多该到学园祭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鹰  你刚刚踩了地雷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地雷？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么  根本没有什么学园祭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道这种单词
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  这学校也有学园祭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓学园祭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是因现充们的现充而起  只为现充而存在的活动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如您所说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  确实对我们来说是个无所谓的活动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把别人都想得跟你们一样好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然身为转学生的小鹰可能不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:04:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但去年的学园祭我可是大显身手了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  理科也看到了哦  去年的星奈学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从理事长那里收到了邀请函  在贵宾席看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你来说明一下  我当时大显身手的华丽英姿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体育祭的时候参加了许多竞技项目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  200米跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借物赛跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,障碍赛跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有吃面包竞赛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马拉松
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是骑马战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有单人能参加的竞技全部参加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后全都拿了第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还真是厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不止体育祭哦  连文化祭也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班里的戏剧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星奈学姐持剑砍翻了坏人们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  因为我是主角嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体育祭和文化祭都是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你一个人看起来气势十足  其他人都被吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但  但是观众席的气氛倒是很热烈的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又跑又跳的学姐的胸部晃来晃去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实男生们都很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戏剧的时候又走光了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不是被我那华丽的表现所吸引的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧有肉的风格的残念活跃方式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是真·残念无双
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准说残念无双什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  我们只能以成熟的方式看着那些现充们的热闹样子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所  所以说小鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当天和我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  邻人部也在文化祭搞些什么活动展出不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  这种时候一般都会以社团名义搞活动的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实那是每次的流程啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就当做为了将来和朋友一起搞活动的时候的练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理科也没意见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥的想法就是我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鹰…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  怎么了夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  没什么  小鹰这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧  邻人部将会参加今年的文化祭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就靠我们的力量来将享受文化祭的现充们给打入地狱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打入地狱是不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  要搞什么展出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹抖咖啡怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么立刻就否定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹抖咖啡难道不是文化祭的王道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这肤浅的笨蛋  接客什么的我怎么可能做得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实夜空没法接客啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不要说女仆了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想象一下夜空穿着女仆装接客的样子  超搞笑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这玩笑开的  噗～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实我没法接客什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你们也是一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接客之类的我还是可以的  虽然没经验
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小鹰去接客的话  大家都会逃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那种事  我只要亲切待人的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鹰学长亲切待人？噗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话你又怎么样啊  能接客吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小看天才发明家志熊理科我就伤脑筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜空学姐  幸村君以前穿的女仆装现在有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得有机会  就穿着女仆装实践一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我要换衣服  请小鹰学长闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以睁开眼睛了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:08:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你的表情  似乎仅仅是认识到理科穿上了女仆服这个事实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外并没有什么特别的感想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  为什么你能读懂我头脑中的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋笨蛋  小鹰学长你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还真的一直闭着眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里应该是偷偷睁眼才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然问为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  你这愚钝布丁  快出去然后重新进房间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近你的嘴还真毒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这蠢木头布丁混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛  你突然干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话快坐去椅子上坐好  混账芋头家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道自己会被人踢却听不明白人家叫你坐下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一只没教养的笨头笨脑的贱狗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这发色就像是吃过肉末咖喱后拉出来的粪便一样的脑袋里\N究竟有没有脑浆也是个疑问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:09:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别以为用傲娇的口吻说话就可以为所欲为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  所以说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁告诉你可以坐在人坐的椅子上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我该坐哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不就有了吗  笨蛋才看不见的椅子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是特地为你端过来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外咖啡的价格是980日元哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是我点的咖啡竟然我要付账  而且好贵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话快脱掉裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边把露出阴部的肮脏丑态暴露在众目睽睽之下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边享受着自己胯间臭味和咖啡香味混合而成的恶魔组合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变态臭虫  哼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算我求你了  这次就放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.29,0:09:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再来也是可以的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才会再来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理科的傲娇女仆怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:10:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里傲娇了  我都受到心理创伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪  我还以为是相当吸引人的接待客人方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸不吸引人先不说  就方向性来说是可行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是方向性也没的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸村君觉得如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在抱歉  我觉得还是不太成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是曾经的女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有掌握到女仆的精髓之类的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  女仆的精髓  那就是对大哥的忠义之心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接  接下来  就让我们看看肉的接客吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？我也要？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是正好吗  我也想看看星奈学姐的接客
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你们没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小鹰  我要换衣服  所以你快到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是闭上眼睛还不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟你已经有两次前科了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了哦  小鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎您回来  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很  很紧的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别色眯眯的盯着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们几个  这么紧的衣服还真亏你们能穿得下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧美毛片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母猪…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请点餐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特制女仆三明治  特制女仆蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特制女仆茶  特制女仆咖啡等等品种齐全哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来杯咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是怎么了  为什么能做到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会也没什么奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  对了  我模仿史黛拉而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  是因为身边有专业的管家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  就是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着管家的工作为什么会知道咖啡店的接客方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是模仿我也对你改观了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这种话啦  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还得施加美味咒语呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒语？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得美味吧  萌啊萌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有一放假就去妹抖咖啡泡一整天啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  妹抖咖啡就甭想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜空  有个问题想问问你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是  那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AB型的你今天的运势最糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心避免伤害到朋友  时刻注意自己的行动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  我又没朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来  小鸠  今天也要补习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长达两周的试炼  在今天就要迎来终焉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次别又不及格了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:13:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占卜馆怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信占卜的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不相信啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过喜欢占卜的人不是很多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是女高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不相信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是被神所选中的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的运势当然是一直都是最好的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.97,0:14:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的没错  肉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的运势一直都是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯哼  你也挺懂的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  你的运势一直都是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说现在就是上限了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再有比现在好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交不了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被同性的同学讨厌挤兑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体育课的时候总是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料理实习和修学旅行分组的时候被说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「柏崎同学和男生组队怎么样哈哈哈」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是这种悲惨的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:15:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这个形态  就是你人生所容许的最高的幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你都在说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星奈学姐  从今以后的生活也请加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星奈大姐头好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别连你们都这么说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs25}占卜馆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs25}鬼屋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过嘛  占卜馆确实不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来夜空相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学时代我连着三个月每天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都把电视报纸杂志上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到的所有的占卜都检查个遍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后每天把那天发生在自己身上的事情详细记录下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着对幸运度进行客观的判定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后全部跟占卜对照统计出结果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中率超过70%的占卜一个都不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定不去相信占卜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到这个份上  反而更像占卜厨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  都做到这份上了还赞成开占卜馆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便乱扯些有的没的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那些真的会相信的低能现充身上骗钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有比这个更爽的买卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你简直就是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜空大姐头真不是盖的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉  作为试验我来为你占卜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝  现在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在烦恼些什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？烦恼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么「汝」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那是关于人际关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？  人际关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来确实…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝身上散发出一层薄薄的紫雾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不安的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据雾的形状我可以看出这是与人有关的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？  好厉害  说中了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:17:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全部都能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝  没错  基本上是乐观向前思考的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是偶尔也会后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你看出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星奈学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外汝还拥有好几个比别人突出的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那些才能都不能好好发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常会有些事情不能如愿进行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时虽然也有乐观的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时而会对自己的行动或者判断产生犹豫而陷入沉思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外虽然平时都很开朗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也有耐不住寂寞的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么你会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  这个叫什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个巴纳姆效应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到那种对谁说都准的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs25\fad(200,200)}你现在在烦恼朋友关系的事情对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs25\fad(200,200)}虽然看起来挺有自信的  但是其实自身有些不安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs25\fad(200,200)}校园生活里会有些琐碎的麻烦发生是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs25\fad(200,200)}最近有些在意体重对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs25\fad(200,200)}有时候会觉得自己挺浪漫的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs25\fad(200,200)}你在等着命运的邂逅对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会错以为那是针对自己的正确诊断的心理现象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.31,0:17:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  超准的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜空竟然这么了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  感觉好像有点开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全中招了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了那么温柔待人友善的你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以教你一个能让人生好转的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  告诉我  告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚零时零分零秒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在屋顶上头顶着装满水的盆子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里一边大声喊叫着一边转三圈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后再用能响彻家里的声音大喊sexy beam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要水不溅出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮的祝福就会附身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝的人生将会有巨大的幸福降临
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  谢谢你夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直误解你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望汝能变得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  星奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被爸爸狠揍了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  为了幸福我豁出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sexy beam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会真的做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs25}去谷歌一下巴纳姆效应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊肉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.11,0:19:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你还说干嘛  你这笨蛋狐狸精
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你？  你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的占卜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在那乱扯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  你也别那么伤心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干傻事惹理事长生气不也是常有的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是说这个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我还真的有点开心的说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:20:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的…真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜空你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  总之先去活动室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼哼  等你很久了  吾之半身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  小鸠…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒  小鸠好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么今天小鸠会在这
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒  小鸠真是天使
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠的天使度世界第一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  小鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能见到小鸠  今天真走运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来幸福降临了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实  幸福真的降临了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:21:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠在我面前降临了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啦  只是补习完了又能来参加社团活动而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.19,0:21:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是因为夜空那乱掰的魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  这可不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个讨厌的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过算了  这次的事看在小鸠份上就原谅你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  别得意过头了  腐肉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.71,0:21:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说回来  文化祭的展示最后决定是占卜馆了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.81,0:21:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姑且是把占卜的资料拿过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之占卜还是保留吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.23,0:21:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来下周是小鸠的生日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.67,0:21:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠的生日？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.19,0:22:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  10月18日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.14,0:22:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话得庆祝了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.70,0:22:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞起来  小鸠的生日派对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.41,0:23:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.63,0:23:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在经历了长久的生死搏斗后我终于再度降临
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补习辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.28,0:23:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了下次不再挂科  你要每天好好学习哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.81,0:23:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼哼  这次是正好阿卡夏记录的状况不太好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.62,0:23:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我去学习
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.14,0:24:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.94,0:24:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.75,0:24:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「虽然是哥哥不过只要有爱的话多几个妹妹也没关系吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.21,0:24:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关系啦  笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:33.29,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光ったはずのあの星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.42,0:22:38.83,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷った雲が邪魔して見えなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:42.23,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何を信じたらいい?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:46.27,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不安定すぎる世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.36,0:22:51.62,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,育った宝物  壊しかけてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.04,0:22:55.24,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失くすのが怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.04,0:22:58.84,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不条理だって  ため息つき
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.16,0:23:02.54,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥かごであがいてた日々
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.66,0:23:08.71,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同じ空を見上げてたんだ  僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:15.19,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の手を握ったとき  握り返してくれたね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:21.78,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繋がったこの手はどんな羽より強いんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.96,0:23:28.23,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼なんてなくたって  もっと高く飛べるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:36.81,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと今なら大丈夫  大空輝く星を掴もう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:33.29,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎闪了一下的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.42,0:22:38.83,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍一犹豫就被云挡住看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:42.23,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底应该相信什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:46.27,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这太不稳定的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.36,0:22:51.62,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孕育出的宝物正在损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.04,0:22:55.24,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于失去实在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.04,0:22:58.84,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不合理  也只能叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.16,0:23:02.54,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鸟笼里挣扎的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.66,0:23:08.71,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰望着同一片天空的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:15.19,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握住你手的时候  你也会握住我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:21.78,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相连着的手比任何翅膀都强大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.96,0:23:28.23,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有翅膀  我们也能飞得更高
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:36.81,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在肯定没问题的  去抓住天上闪耀着的星星吧

